abstract: The recall involves more than 60 million cans of dog and cat food sold under dozens of brand names.
snippet: The recall involves more than 60 million cans of dog and cat food sold under dozens of brand names.
lead_paragraph: More than 60 million cans and pouches of dog and cat food sold under dozens of brand names were recalled on Saturday after being linked to the deaths of 10 animals.

headline.main: Pet Food Is Recalled After Link to Animal Deaths
headline.print_headline: Canned Pet Food Is Recalled After Link to Animal Deaths
